with $\lambda\equiv s^2(m_{\rm DM})\langle \sigma v^2\rangle /H(m_{\rm DM})$ where $s(m_{\rm DM})=\frac{2\pi^2}{45} g_{*s} m^3_{\rm DM}$ and $H(m_{\rm DM})=\sqrt{\frac{\pi^2}{90} g_*} \,\frac{m^2_{\rm DM}}{M_P}$.  
